Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's monstrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been waiting for you, Seto...\N And I welcome you Duelists as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept the Duel with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute. But what'll happen to us if we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bring up an {\i1}excellent{\i0} point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you'll be {\i1}exchanged{\i0} with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll wander the Cyber World for {\i1}all eternity{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! That's low!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our {\i1}revenge{\i0} against you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deck Master - Deepsea Warrior"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can beat us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll let you leave this Virtual Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you to refuse our challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unfortunately for you people, we will not permit you to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only {\i1}scumbags{\i0} would think of such a low plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your first opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take what your friend there just said as an agreement to Duel against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!\N-Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Five! Where'd you send everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Big Five! How dare you make a fool of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my brother and everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi! Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I? Where's Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you're my {\i1}very important{\i0} guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy this world for the time being!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, the first matchup will be between Yugi Mutou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the first member of the Big Five, the Deepsea Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this also Virtual Reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want us to {\i1}Duel{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be the first opponent you face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a loyal subordinate of Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have taken over, raided and merged countless companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my great skill and abilities while imagining it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have taken on the form of the Deepsea Warrior, as you see before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I {\i1}myself{\i0} am the Deck Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} why you made the Deck Master System!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I lost my body because of you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a pseudo form made to get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you underestimate this world just because it's virtual, you're in for some pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, it's about time I make do on my grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown {\i1}fed up{\i0}\N with lingering in this Cyber World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get myself a body as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the youth and energy of that young body while you still {\i1}can{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and my colleagues will greet your friends in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're going to go after Anzu and Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we have no reason to Duel with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have to beat him fast and go find Anzu and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, it seems there's no other choice but to accept this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I have no intentions of getting involved with your so-called "revenge",
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we should get this started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Type-B Yugi, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou... Our references told us that you have two alternating thinking patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Duelist with two thinking minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's essential to do your research before issuing a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say, "If you take interest in your enemy, you cross the white line of victory and reign supreme".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to use your deck in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin, you will have to make a {\i1}new{\i0} deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the card data owned by Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply touch the cards you desire with your finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Big Five... How exactly are they related to this kid called Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then choose one of them as your Deck Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He told me to choose one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I have no idea what abilities each individual card possesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gazelle and Berfomet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think they'd be a good choice for the Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then should I try for the Black Magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, I'll go with the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you chose Kuriboh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Kuriboh just came out on his own...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but once your Deck Master appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you cannot change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "Count on me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. I'll believe you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master is Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, my Deck Master is the Deepsea Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, preparation time has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you experience the Duel of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be my turn first. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Monster in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first step is okay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only the first step of my formation strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's also a fine trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I figured he'd have something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he did nothing except place a Monster in Defense, which is your common move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he must have a special plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to my research,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Type B Yugi will disregard all other options and choose to attack head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He lives by the motion, "One must take action at all costs."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let him set his formation the way he's planning to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll destroy that Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Retrained Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrained Elf Swordsman attacks your Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is exactly as we learned of of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Children truly {\i0}are{\i1} simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, I activate its Reverse Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposing player must discard one card from their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Ashingrai is beaten in battle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you still have an Ashingrai in your deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can Special Summon another\Nfrom your deck in Reverse Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then shuffle the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about this, Yugi Mutou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ashingrai you went to the trouble of beating is back once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you begun to read my strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, they're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true this scenery is beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this is all only an illusion, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... this water is so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on Earth am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I can't believe those Big Five jerks actually came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, if anything, at least they've got tenacity down-pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Big Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna Duel, get yer asses out here and face me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't got all day, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're off hiding somewhere and watchin' me, ain't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop stalling for time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna ignore me, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry up and beat Malik so I can rescue Mai from that weird trick he used on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the time to be wasting waiting for you punks to decide to Duel me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna do it, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, we're still getting lost in this maze despite it being virtual!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks the same no matter how far we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Otogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this virtual room a little too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we'd better find Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} soon. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, they made this Virtual Space so vivid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed this Virtual Space does look quite real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just a copy of my Solid Vision in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who that Noah guy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First that huge mobile floating fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now the virtual system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't things a little brat can come up with on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I highly doubt those Big Five scumbags had the strength to pull this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to assume that there is somebody more powerful backing them up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the intentions of \Ndestroying Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, can we escape from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I know the basics of this system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be an emergency exit programmed in here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably look like a window or a door, to given an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ipiria, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any player who successfully Summons Ipiria can draw one card from his deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice process, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, during the Renaissance, an Italian political thinker once said the following:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There are three conditions for victory."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first being, "Seize the chance."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Ipiria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I successfully Summoned this card, I am permitted to draw a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then switch the Ashingrai I have in Reverse Defense Mode into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing with the the conditions for victory, the second is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maintain your expenses."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this change of formation, I activate its Reverse Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent player has to throw\None card from his hand into the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though this Ashingrai doesn't have very strong Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can still perform quite a few tricks that can be used in many different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both Ashingrai and Ipiria have 500 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he tempting me to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't make it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't save Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}\Nif we keep running like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! There's no exit here because it's a virtual world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means if there's no exit from the beginning, there won't be one at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell? That means we'll be running around here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really a simple matter then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's not an exit, we {\i1}make{\i0} one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just gotta smash through these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This wall's nothing but special screening designed to intimidate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are really just the walls of that mobile fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can break through here, we can go out from the back stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That ax isn't virtual?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why was he able to grab it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Virtual Space, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have to search for the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They've got me surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubts.\N That's the program used as an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the orphanage where my big brother and I stayed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bad taste...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What possible reason could Noah have to program this in the Virtual World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he tempting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or just trying to bluff me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit... I'm falling into his pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm starting to think too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what his goal is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't just stand here and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The others are in danger and waiting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while I'm just standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Fusion card?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let's decide this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fuse Berfomet and Illusion Beast Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winged Illusion Beast Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate the Magic Card, Quick Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Winged Illusion Beast Chimera to attack Ipiria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third step of the conditions for victory states...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tempt your enemies to follow the path of self-destruction."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it! I activate my Deck Master Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Deck Master Ability...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Special Ability is called Reflector Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use two Monsters as sacrifices,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make the opponent's attack\Nbounce back directly to the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How {\i1}was{\i0} it?! That was my Deck Master Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now that this is no ordinary Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In pain, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wounds you get in this Virtual Space
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be taken by your brain as real ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And add the burden to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for your friends to Duel in the other Spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aside, I wonder if your {\i1}other weaker{\i0} friends can take such suffering...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you {\i1}worried{\i0} about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Duel can't last much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right! We should beat him as soon as possible and get to where the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(127,112)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many are beaten,\NMonsters still show up one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Revival Combo of Deepsea Warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,starts to get Yugi frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, who were relayed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to another Virtual Space\Nmeet their past selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} and the others are\Nattacked by Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}I{\i0} am caught by Cyclops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:22:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and rescue us, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Terrifying Revival Combo"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise